{"tid":1302573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人善忘，但今次唔可以","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:52:26.000Z","uid":247482,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a65c3492bd8683e90b6a94494fd9f762eeea1de6","tid":1302573,"uid":247482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:55:10.000Z","msg":"保皇內鬥，港共疑似龜縮，散仔協會縮沙,TVB失廣告...等等<br />\n開始好消息多過壞消息，形勢好似一片大好...?<br />\n<br />\n而事實係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>撤回惡法</strong><br />\n死都唔講就係想再推，而且係想三個月都慳番<br />\n612為阻止二讀我地係負上沉重代價，有人捱子彈有人被捕（仲持續緊）<br />\n<strong>不起訴，不秋後算帳</strong><br />\n拒絕, 照告照拉<br />\n<strong>成立獨立調查委員會</strong><br />\n拒絕，監警會做完報告會比&quot;建議&quot;警隊架喇<br />\n而且佢呼籲&quot;所有參加過呢一系列事件既人&quot;提供資料for監警會做呢個&quot;建議&quot;<br />\n<strong>立即實現雙普選</strong><br />\n答都費事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現時為止乜都爭取唔到，反而仲失去左好多</span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆TVB繼續搞無壞，但記住呢D唔係主線<br />\n我知大家都好攰，但希望有集體活動既話點都要繼續行出黎<br />\n<br />\n為左仲比狗咬住同先行一步既手足，我地無鬆懈既理由！"},{"pid":"d15cc73e962677367e3d209d7de595c17ab41083","tid":1302573,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"178741a81954378e3fe256f858b484bb34de06a8","tid":1302573,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5371a653b603d9320e18830ceaf9e7dc31c918","tid":1302573,"uid":164442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上水遊行路線更新</strong></span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302535</a><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11941804c59a3d6ede9b3c0cb4092da2403da68","tid":1302573,"uid":193565,"li